  <summary date="2018-07-23T16:10:44Z" status="Introduced in House">Sunshine Protection Act of 2018

The bill amends the Uniform Time Act of 1966 to make daylight savings time the new, permanent standard time.

States with areas exempt from daylight savings time may choose the standard time for those areas.</summary>
